Description: The standard Ibishu 1.5L I4 in this car creates a jaw-dropping 670 horsepower and 900Nm of torque, with the help of a NOMI radiator, part stripping, a massive turbocharger, and a 6-speed race transmission fitted to an AWD race configuration. Okudai GZ03 wheels, and an Okudai body kit complete the look of the car, and compliment it's special paint job.
